 Galvatron smiled. "Wonderful, absolutely wonderful." He walked over the the 
main operating computer. He added in the coordinates of all the known enemy 
bases he had scanned while on his little romp with Rodimus. They werent far 
from Megatrons base. The maximals were far away but that would not pose to 
big of a problem.

::another pod activates::
 The medium sized pod pulled himself out. He looked around and saw a few 
familiar faces. "My name is Quilldart...yes my memory circuts are still 
finctional. How is the lab did it survive the crash?"
Galvatron nodded not even turning his head. "Yes Quilldart your precious lab 
is still there." Quilldart with a Bat for a beast mode now, was Galvatron's 
researcher and scientist of sorts. He's who he turned to to think up any new 
toys that may help in the war.  Quilldart with glee ran out of the room into 
the lab and started to clean it up.
  He turned to Empath.."how are our friends coming along."

--part1_2f.29cb4b04.2a5c4f96_boundary
